<p><a name="Specifications" id="Specifications"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=BIOS&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13" title="Edit section: Specifications">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Specifications</span></h3>
